  "short_description": "BounceShot is a Action Puzzle FPS where all shots must be bounced. Position your body and weapon to fire projectiles that bounce around corners, hit switches on ceilings, or strike unsuspecting droids. Race to each level's exit portal in order to get the best time. Scores reward speed and style!",
